No matter your interest, the CES Conference Program has something for you.&nbsp; Scan the entire program to find these and other sessions and tracks:<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE><STRONG><A href="http://www.cesweb.org/conferenceprogram/search/results.asp?categoryID=2077 "><STRONG><IMG style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" border=0 hspace=5 src="/images/content/CEAResearchsummit225pw.jpg" width=108 height=42>CEA Research Summit at International CES</STRONG></A>&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR></STRONG>Get ahead of the trends that are defining the tech industry, and be first to see the technologies that will drive the industry through 2012.<BR><BR><IMG style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" border=0 hspace=5 src="/images/content/CONNECTIONS-Summit.jpg" width=106 height=55><A href="http://www.cesweb.org/conferenceprogram/search/results.asp?categoryID=2081 "><STRONG>CONNECTIONS™ Summit: Monetizing Connectivity in the Digital Home</STRONG></A>&nbsp; <BR>Gain C-level insights and make some connections of your own with leading companies in the digital living space. International research firm Parks Associates presents consumer and industry trends, new business models and technologies, and growth opportunities for companies developing products and services for the digital home.<BR><BR><IMG style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 3px" border=0 hspace=3 src="/images/content/JEDEC.jpg" width=116 height=33><A href="http://www.cesweb.org/conferenceprogram/search/results.asp?categoryID=2098 "><STRONG>Memory Matters: Memory Solutions for Consumer Products and Mobile Devices</STRONG><BR></A>Faster, smaller, better. Ever-increasing expectations for mobile device and consumer product performance are driving the need for versatile memory solutions. Discover how technological advancements and new standards can enhance performance, reduce power usage and enable compact form factors now and in the future. </BLOCKQUOTE><br />
