<div class="sub-content-header">Designated Passenger Pickup/Drop-off Areas at LVCC</div>
<br />

<P><IMG style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" border=0 hspace=5 src="/images/photos/GenTransp190X136.jpg" width=131 height=109>Are you picking up or dropping off a friend or colleague at the LVCC? To alleviate traffic congestion and increase safety, we have designated portions of the LVCC, Silver 3 Lot and Gold Lot for privately owned vehicles to pick up and drop off passengers. Curbside access will no longer be permitted</P>
<P>For access closest to South Halls, plan to use the Silver 3 Lot by entering off of Paradise Road. For access to North and Central Halls, plan to use the Gold Lot at the corner of Paradise and Convention Center Drive by entering off of Convention Center Drive. Note: Drivers must remain with their cars; no parking allowed. <BR><BR><A href="http://cesweb.org/hotelTravel/cars.asp">Get more information on 2012 CES parking and transportation.<BR></A></P><br />
