<div class="sub-content-header">Entertainment Apps Conference</div>
<br />

<P><IMG style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" border=0 hspace=5 src="/images/content/EntertainmentApps-banner2.jpg" width=140 height=130>On December 1, the <A href="http://www.variety.com/events/2011/entertainment-apps-conference/" target=_blank>Entertainment Apps Conference</A> will focus on efforts to develop new business models and strategies for monetizing long-form media content through self-contained apps. Bringing together executives in the interactive, marketing and distribution departments of movie and TV production and distribution companies, as well as third-party developers with apps platform providers, embedded apps platform developers, technology provider and consumer electronics device makers. <BR><BR>Confirmed speakers include: Colin Helms, MTV Digital Media; Dustin Callif, Tool North America; Andrew Osis, Poynt Corporation; and Steve Felter of GameSalad.</P>
<P>The Consumer Electronics Association has arranged a special 10 percent discount off registration for its members. <A href="http://www.regonline.com/Register/Checkin.aspx?EventID=1013925" target=_blank>Register today </A>with code CEA.</P><br />
